measure.CatchLine: Prohibits residential landlords from charging an applicant screening charge.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: The Act bans applicant screening fees for tenants. (Flesch Readability Score: 71.8). 
	Prohibits residential landlords from charging an applicant screening charge.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to residential applicant screening charges; amending ORS 90.100, 90.140, 90.295, 90.297, 90.302, 90.555, 90.634, 90.680, 215.490, 456.259 and 646A.614.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to residential applicant screening charges.
